profile:
'Hygge' is a Danish term and describes an environment that is comfortable, cozy and safe.  It is a space that allows you to enjoy and be yourself.

We strive to bring the essence of Hygge to the homes of our clientele.

Hygge Homes operates in Vancouver, Nanaimo, Nanoose Bay and Parksville.  Whether you are looking to remodel your bathroom or kitchen or if you are looking to build an extension to your home or build a garage, we can help you to achieve your goals quickly and with quality finishes.  We and our partners cover all types of interior and exterior work ranging from framing, finish carpentry, electrical, plumbing, drywalling, painting, windows and doors and more.

Reach out today to arrange a free consultation of your next project.
We look forward to hearing from you!
services:

Carmana Home Improvements, located in beautiful Qualicum Beach, British Columbia, is a full service company with years of combined experience in the construction industry. Specializing in residential renovations, our goal is to provide superior service for our satisfied customers. Our history working with return clients in the Lower Mainland has given us a top notch reputation, with the flexibility to carry out successful projects both in Qualicum Beach and in the Lower Mainland.

Your renovation begins at an initial site meeting to learn your requirements and discuss relevant work into a plan. We pride ourselves in understanding each clientâ€™s specific needs. Through careful planning and by trusting a professional you are on your way to ensuring a successful project.
